item.title: Regex
item.description: . - Any Character Except New Line \d - Digit (0-9) \D - Not a Digit (0-9) \w - Word Character (a-z, A-Z, 0-9, _) \W - Not a Word Character \s - Whitespace (space, tab, newline) \S - Not Whitespace (space, tab, newline) \b - Word Boundary \B - Not a Word Boundary ^ - Beginning of a String $ - End of a String [] - Matches Characters in brackets [^ ] - Matches Characters NOT in brackets | - Either Or ( ) - Group Quantifiers: * - 0 or More + - 1 or More ?
